{"tid":2403090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聯合國特使警告緬甸 勿過度使用武力","createTime":"2021-02-11T01:37:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T02:22:02.000Z","uid":3747,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e4a413a2b06c6c5fd3e584d7d47a6ff612bf8ef4","tid":2403090,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T01:37:20.000Z","msg":"聯合國緬甸人權特別報告員安德魯斯(Thomas Andrews)今天(10日)在日內瓦(Geneva)發布聲明說，根據國際法，緬甸安全部隊和警察，有義務避免動用過度武力來對付和平示威者。在傳出緬甸軍警動用致命武器對付示威群眾之後，聯合國表達關切。<br />\n<br />\n聲明指出，「緬甸軍方人員和警察有必要知道，『奉命行事』無法為犯下的暴行辯護，而任何這類的辯護都會失敗，不管他們是站在指揮鏈當中的哪個位置。」<br />\n<br />\n安德魯斯指出，自從2月1日以來，已經紀錄到有好幾百人遭到任意拘押，有些甚至被禁止與外界接觸。<br />\n<br />\n緬甸武裝部隊總司令敏昂萊(Min Aung Hlaing)的軍隊在2月1日清晨展開突襲政變，拘押了緬甸實質領導人翁山蘇姬(Aung San Suu Kyi)等多位政治領袖，奪取政權。<br />\n<br />\n隨後緬甸各地引爆10年來最大規模的示威風潮，軍事當局在9日展開強力驅散行動，包括動用水砲、橡皮子彈，甚至真槍實彈，最少造成4名示威者中彈，其中1人傷勢嚴重有生命危險。<br />\n<br />\n大示威今天進入連續第五天，民眾不畏當局的威嚇，勇敢上街抗議， 反對軍事政變。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2091587\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rti.org.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2Fid%2F2091587&d=i0%2FHWd2N8RLCa1A1b4xPLHyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=cf27eb52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2091587</a>"},{"pid":"55e826b13d6c3307f7226580b36239f8839349c0","tid":2403090,"uid":256837,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T01:38:42.000Z","msg":"香港嗰陣點講㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d94ce857561be24641ec47d3216c0d7394e4816","tid":2403090,"uid":7369,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"55e826b13d6c3307f7226580b36239f8839349c0","tid":2403090,"uid":256837,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T01:38:42.000Z","msg":"香港嗰陣點講㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T01:39:45.000Z","msg":"唔多覺有出過聲"},{"pid":"e17cd7a88985f06d984dbda1a01c9dbd7cd23ed4","tid":2403090,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T01:40:52.000Z","msg":"警告師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efc4bf80a6d52ac4d5d74ad01925e6f1ed62e58b","tid":2403090,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T01:50:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc43e2621533ca7206552bc41c9835e92cf79fc4","tid":2403090,"uid":45934,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T01:55:41.000Z","msg":"係咪習習比左greenlight<br />\nBiden 又話制裁<br />\nUN又出警告"},{"pid":"3d32b881deccd56ac42b463ac96038774b5ba63e","tid":2403090,"uid":358542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T01:57:18.000Z","msg":"搵個緬甸版美心太子女，搞掂"},{"pid":"43a11364cd1a0c6a1dd63b0d0f013f7a649b313d","tid":2403090,"uid":2223,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T01:57:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRDRGjyqTrSeBF9vrmtySdP0n6DDhfRhfI80w&amp;usqp=CAU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcRDRGjyqTrSeBF9vrmtySdP0n6DDhfRhfI80w%26usqp%3DCAU&h=164f62ca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"309bc3ebf5a41e3b2c616b9ff9b2ee63f215188c","tid":2403090,"uid":57674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55e826b13d6c3307f7226580b36239f8839349c0","tid":2403090,"uid":256837,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T01:38:42.000Z","msg":"香港嗰陣點講㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T01:57:59.000Z","msg":"無講過"},{"pid":"ca0856e6c793a0bc091afcbcf5c3298fd646f3e0","tid":2403090,"uid":80103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T02:20:01.000Z","msg":"警告師"},{"pid":"ed965f06203380573cd894e114da7b957af3b2da","tid":2403090,"uid":32588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T02:21:39.000Z","msg":"一日中俄有否決權<br />\n聯合國咩都唔